-- St. Mary Land to acquire Texas oil-gas properties
-- 
-- Wed Nov 1, 2006 8:57pm EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2006/11/02/us-energy-stmaryland-idUSWEN880820061102

 

 SAN FRANCISCO  (Reuters) - St. Mary Land & Exploration Co. ( SM.N ) on Wednesday said it signed an agreement to purchase oil and gas properties in west Texas for $250 million cash from undisclosed private parties. 

 Denver-based St. Mary said the properties in the Midland Basin have proved net reserves of 78.1 billion cubic feet equivalent -- BCFE -- of proved net reserves producing about 16 million cubic feet equivalent -- MMCFED -- a day. The deal is scheduled to close by December 15, St. Mary said.